title: [River's Rest, Festival Grounds]
description: A gravel and shell path winds down a gentle slope, running parallel to the Tempest River, whose waters can be seen glittering beyond a fringe of grass and cattails.  Overhead, an oilcloth banner spans the path, supported by a pair of garland-wrapped poles flanked by unlit torches.

A gravel and shell path winds down a gentle slope, running parallel to the Tempest River, whose waters can be seen glittering beyond a dark fringe of grass and cattails.  Overhead, an oilcloth banner supported by garland-wrapped poles spans the path and is illuminated by torches on each side.
